text:
Receptionist was lovely and made the process of registering quick and painless.

Doctor that we saw was friendly and professional. I brought my 9yr old daughter to see him today (so sorry I didn't catch your name!) and he was speedy with diagnosing the problem as well as had a great bed side manner that made my daughter feel at ease. Thank you!

It's a pleasant surprise for me when I got the medicine for my family member. The friendliness and the proactiveness of the staff is much better as compared to the past. Many thanks to Kalai for making it easy. Please keep it up!

Few days ago I went to this medical center because not well... doctor and the nurses who work there very good... especially nurse Kalai Vani who are working there was very caring and kindness person.... highly recommend
Good clinic. Open on Saturday and Sunday.
The staff was very friendly, on time, very fast  to go for my turn. Recommended to go again ðŸ‘Œ Great service.
